      "parameters": {
        "height": 464,
        "width": 368,
        "content": "## ðŸŽ¯ AI Lead Research & Email Generator\n\n**Purpose**: Advanced lead generation workflow that researches companies using Perplexity AI and generates personalized outreach emails\n\n**How it works**:\n1. **Manual Trigger**: Start with company name/website\n2. **Company Research**: Use Perplexity to research company details, recent news, and pain points\n3. **Contact Research**: Find key decision makers and their contact information\n4. **Email Generation**: Create personalized emails based on research findings\n5. **CRM Integration**: Store all data in Google Sheets for tracking and follow-up\n\n**Key Features**:\n- âœ… Automated company intelligence gathering\n- âœ… Pain point identification for targeted messaging\n- âœ… Personalized email generation\n- âœ… Contact enrichment with decision maker details\n- âœ… Full CRM tracking in Google Sheets\n- âœ… Follow-up scheduling and status tracking\n\n**Value Proposition**: Transform cold outreach into warm, research-backed conversations that convert better"
      },
